  <section id="which-environments-are-found-in-the-ganges" class="slider-slice_container paragraph-container">
    <section class="text_link_carousel " aria-labelledby="carousel-heading">
            <div class="article_wrapper text-link-heading-container">
                <h3>
            Which environments are found in the Ganges
        </h3>
                        <p>
            <p>The Ganges River basin is the most populated in the world, home to more than 650 million people, and some unique endangered and endemic&nbsp;wildlife.</p>
        </p>
              </div>
            <div class="splide">
        <div class="splide__track article_wrapper">
