                                                                                  <h4>Keeping the Ganges river flowing</h4>
                                        <div class="description-container">
                      The first step to managing water resources fairly and sustainably is understanding the river’s natural cycles of river flows that change across the seasons
                                                                      <div class="find-out-more-container">
                          <a href="">
                                                          Find out more
                                                        <i class="fa fa-arrow-right"></i>
                          </a>
                        </div>
                                          </div>
                  </figcaption>
                </figure>
              </li>
                                                                    <li class="splide__slide">
                <figure>
                  <img src="https://www.wwf.org.uk/sites/default/files/styles/square_xs/public/2016-09/Medium_WW22292.jpg?h=dc0d9529&amp;itok=-cPVPNrs"
                       srcset="https://www.wwf.org.uk/sites/default/files/styles/square_xs/public/2016-09/Medium_WW22292.jpg?h=dc0d9529&amp;itok=-cPVPNrs 320w,
                         https://www.wwf.org.uk/sites/default/files/styles/square_s/public/2016-09/Medium_WW22292.jpg?h=dc0d9529&amp;itok=gKFBajNQ 640w,
                         https://www.wwf.org.uk/sites/default/files/styles/square_m_new/public/2016-09/Medium_WW22292.jpg?h=dc0d9529&amp;itok=lI-pcYPr 768w,
                         https://www.wwf.org.uk/sites/default/files/styles/square_l/public/2016-09/Medium_WW22292.jpg?h=dc0d9529&amp;itok=Nze9m5cA 1024w,
                         https://www.wwf.org.uk/sites/default/files/styles/square_l/public/2016-09/Medium_WW22292.jpg?h=dc0d9529&amp;itok=Nze9m5cA 1200w,
                         https://www.wwf.org.uk/sites/default/files/styles/square_l/public/2016-09/Medium_WW22292.jpg?h=dc0d9529&amp;itok=Nze9m5cA 1440w,
                         https://www.wwf.org.uk/sites/default/files/styles/square_l/public/2016-09/Medium_WW22292.jpg?h=dc0d9529&amp;itok=Nze9m5cA 1536w"
                       alt=""
                       sizes="(max-width:320px) 100vw,
                       (max-width: 640px) 90vw,
                       (max-width: 1024px) 75vw,
                       (max-width:1440px) 50vw,
                       33vw"
